WEBVTT

00:20.080 --> 00:21.920
THATCHED COTTAGE

00:25.240 --> 00:26.080
Come on.

00:33.240 --> 00:35.040
Winter's just around the corner.

00:35.760 --> 00:39.160
Who knows if we'll see Changyu
by New Year's.

00:39.800 --> 00:41.360
You old woman,

00:41.880 --> 00:43.400
no vision at all.

00:44.240 --> 00:46.840
Changyu's out there doing great things.

00:46.920 --> 00:49.760
What's all this fuss about
coming home for New Year's?

00:49.840 --> 00:51.080
You old one.

00:51.160 --> 00:53.720
You just went off and fought one battle.
How much more vision do you have than me?

00:55.000 --> 00:56.240
Don't kid yourself.

00:56.320 --> 00:59.720
During my time, the horses I saw
outnumber the steamed buns you've eaten.

00:59.800 --> 01:01.520
My vision's opened up wide.

01:01.600 --> 01:03.080
You're just a horse watcher.

01:03.160 --> 01:04.160
What else would you see but horses?

01:04.239 --> 01:05.800
-What else could you possibly see?
-Who's there?

01:21.320 --> 01:22.840
-Ning!
-Quick!

01:22.920 --> 01:24.880
-Quick, inside.
-Hurry, come in. Let's go.

01:24.960 --> 01:26.040
Quick!

01:27.360 --> 01:28.480
Quick. This way.

01:31.000 --> 01:31.840
Hide.

02:37.400 --> 02:38.360
Xie Qi.

02:39.440 --> 02:40.280
Xie Qi?

02:44.720 --> 02:46.640
Uncle, Auntie, it's safe outside now.

02:47.320 --> 02:48.560
Really safe?

02:53.520 --> 02:54.840
Where's Ms. Yu?

02:56.800 --> 02:57.760
Ms. Yu?

02:57.840 --> 02:58.960
-Ms. Yu!
-Bao'er.

02:59.040 --> 02:59.960
Bao'er.

04:32.480 --> 04:37.400
ADAPTED FROM THE NOVEL ZHU YU
BY TUAN ZI LAI XI ON JJWXC.NET

04:44.520 --> 04:46.960
You're saying she held a knife
to her own throat,

04:47.040 --> 04:48.320
threatening you to release Yu Bao'er?

04:49.400 --> 04:50.240
Yes.

04:51.200 --> 04:53.960
Whatever arm you used to strike her,
cut off that arm.

04:54.680 --> 04:56.440
If the lady doesn't wake up,

04:56.520 --> 04:58.000
you'll be buried with her.

04:58.080 --> 04:59.240
I thank your grace.

05:09.760 --> 05:10.680
You're awake.

05:15.720 --> 05:17.120
You two physicians, come here.

05:22.680 --> 05:23.520
Save her immediately.

05:24.200 --> 05:25.560
If anything happens to her,

05:26.240 --> 05:28.240
none of you will leave alive.

05:28.320 --> 05:29.760
She has a knife wound.

05:29.840 --> 05:32.280
The wound burst open,
causing a high fever.

05:32.360 --> 05:34.400
Then figure out a solution now.

05:34.480 --> 05:35.320
-Yes.
-Yes.

05:35.400 --> 05:36.560
We are on it. On it now.

05:37.840 --> 05:39.440
Don't kill innocent people.

05:40.440 --> 05:41.680
If you kill them…

05:42.840 --> 05:44.720
I don't wnat to live either.

05:46.960 --> 05:48.120
You can't die.

05:48.640 --> 05:51.280
As long as you live,
I'll promise you anything.

05:56.680 --> 05:57.640
Qianqian.

05:59.320 --> 06:00.240
Qianqian!

06:01.720 --> 06:04.400
Bring me every physician
from miles around!

06:08.600 --> 06:09.520
You.

06:17.200 --> 06:18.120
Next one.

06:19.160 --> 06:20.000
Get in.

06:22.360 --> 06:23.400
Next one.

06:25.560 --> 06:26.960
-Spare me!
-You.

06:27.920 --> 06:29.280
-Spare me!
-Get in.

06:29.360 --> 06:30.480
And you.

06:32.040 --> 06:35.720
LEGACY OF WISDOM AND LOYALTY

06:39.440 --> 06:41.640
She's… She's awake.

06:41.720 --> 06:42.600
She's awake.

06:43.440 --> 06:44.480
Qianqian.

06:52.040 --> 06:53.120
You're finally awake.

07:08.520 --> 07:10.440
You promised me you wouldn't kill anyone.

07:12.360 --> 07:13.400
How could you…

07:18.080 --> 07:19.920
-Guards!
-Here.

07:20.640 --> 07:21.520
Wake them up.

07:21.600 --> 07:22.560
Yes, sir.

07:26.280 --> 07:28.240
Get up.

07:30.480 --> 07:32.120
-Get up.
-Forgive us, my lady.

07:32.200 --> 07:34.520
We're unharmed. We've disturbed your rest.

07:34.600 --> 07:35.560
See?

07:36.440 --> 07:37.320
Playing dead.

07:38.320 --> 07:41.480
I just knocked them out,
scared them a little.

07:43.400 --> 07:44.920
In a backwater like this,

07:46.000 --> 07:47.600
if you don't threaten their lives,

07:47.680 --> 07:51.560
these quacks
won't give their all to save you.

07:54.880 --> 07:56.200
Every word you said,

07:57.120 --> 07:58.240
I remember.

08:04.000 --> 08:05.280
Send them back.

08:07.080 --> 08:08.440
-Get up.
-Get up.

08:09.040 --> 08:09.880
Get up.

08:12.720 --> 08:14.000
Move.

08:14.080 --> 08:15.280
Faster. Go.

08:15.360 --> 08:16.200
Faster.

08:19.400 --> 08:20.360
This knife

08:21.440 --> 08:22.880
almost cost you your life.

08:24.760 --> 08:27.000
Why did you step
in front of that little brat?

08:31.160 --> 08:34.960
-Mother!
-Take out the little one, not the woman.

08:36.559 --> 08:37.400
Don't move.

08:37.480 --> 08:39.840
Go quickly. Find Uncle Xie Qi.

08:39.919 --> 08:42.039
-Go.
-Mother!

08:42.120 --> 08:43.400
Run.

08:49.640 --> 08:52.360
If you dare loose those arrows,
I'll kill myself.

08:52.440 --> 08:54.160
See how you explain that to that madman.

08:55.120 --> 08:56.760
Even a tiger won't eat its own cubs.

08:58.680 --> 09:00.400
You'd kill your own son.

09:01.840 --> 09:04.160
I don't know what these people see in you.

09:05.120 --> 09:06.640
Aren't you afraid one day,

09:07.800 --> 09:09.080
you'll kill them too?

09:10.760 --> 09:11.800
In the end,

09:12.880 --> 09:14.640
you're still angry
I tried to kill Yu Bao'er.

09:15.160 --> 09:16.720
You're clever enough

09:17.600 --> 09:20.600
to know Xie Zheng would use him
to control the realm.

09:28.400 --> 09:30.400
This child came at the wrong time.

09:32.280 --> 09:33.720
Just focus on recovering.

09:34.440 --> 09:37.120
Once I ascend the throne
and rule over all,

09:37.640 --> 09:41.320
we'll have as many as you like.

09:48.000 --> 09:49.000
Right.

09:49.520 --> 09:50.920
I've prepared a surprise for you.

09:53.600 --> 09:54.720
Come in.

09:58.080 --> 09:58.920
My lady.

10:01.160 --> 10:02.400
Zisu.

10:02.480 --> 10:05.040
You're alive. Thank goodness.

10:05.120 --> 10:06.480
You're finally awake.

10:07.000 --> 10:07.840
See?

10:07.920 --> 10:10.200
I brought back the maid who knows

10:10.280 --> 10:11.280
how to care for you best.

10:12.160 --> 10:14.800
With her here, you'll recover in no time.

10:33.040 --> 10:35.760
UNRIVALED IN MERIT

10:42.360 --> 10:45.120
Changyu, are you settling in well
at the general's residence?

10:45.200 --> 10:46.200
It's fine.

10:46.280 --> 10:48.840
Just too few people, not lively enough.

10:48.920 --> 10:51.240
I've never lived in such a big place.

10:51.320 --> 10:52.560
My voice echoes when I speak.

10:52.640 --> 10:54.200
To be honest,

10:54.280 --> 10:56.040
I'm afraid to call out at night.

10:56.560 --> 10:57.920
It's quite eerie.

10:59.920 --> 11:01.320
Bengong… No.

11:02.520 --> 11:03.600
Your Highness.

11:03.680 --> 11:04.880
"Your Highness"?

11:04.960 --> 11:07.120
I prefer it
when you call me "Miss Bengong".

11:08.000 --> 11:09.440
Oh, I have something for you.

11:22.320 --> 11:23.560
Come, open it.

11:27.600 --> 11:29.960
I picked out these clothes
especially for you.

11:31.840 --> 11:33.080
And some jewelry too.

11:34.280 --> 11:35.800
Take it. Wear them when you have time.

11:35.880 --> 11:38.840
Even if we're generals now,
we can still be pretty young ladies.

11:38.920 --> 11:41.680
But this is too much, too precious.

11:41.760 --> 11:44.240
Between us, don't say such distant things.

11:44.320 --> 11:46.760
-Try this on.
-This one I'm wearing is fine.

11:46.840 --> 11:50.040
-Just try it. It's so pretty.
-I'm fine in this. Really.

11:50.120 --> 11:51.800
-Don't try it now.
-Just try it once.

11:51.880 --> 11:53.880
-No, really.
-Changyu.

11:54.400 --> 11:56.520
-Just try it. It'll look great.
-I'm not used to clothes like this.

11:56.600 --> 11:57.640
I am sure.

12:03.160 --> 12:04.720
-It's gorgeous.
-Let me see it.

12:13.280 --> 12:14.520
Our Flower-Adorned General,

12:15.040 --> 12:16.880
with such beauty,

12:16.960 --> 12:18.880
the Marquis of Wu'an is truly fortunate.

12:21.040 --> 12:22.560
Your Highness, General.

12:24.000 --> 12:27.560
In two days, officials will arrive to
instruct the General in court etiquette.

12:28.480 --> 12:29.400
What?

12:30.280 --> 12:33.760
OFFICE OF RITES AND CEREMONIES

12:38.240 --> 12:39.680
Standing there like a lump of wood.

12:40.320 --> 12:41.400
Just in the way.

12:42.560 --> 12:45.600
How rude are you.
You're the one who bumped into him.

12:47.320 --> 12:48.440
What's it to you?

12:48.960 --> 12:49.800
-You…
-Wu.

12:50.840 --> 12:53.280
Let it go. Better to avoid trouble.

12:56.040 --> 12:57.360
Thank you, Wu, for speaking up.

13:00.280 --> 13:03.040
We've been stuck here doing menial labor
for almost a year now.

13:03.880 --> 13:06.000
No idea when His Majesty
will see fit to employ us again.

13:07.120 --> 13:09.960
I've almost forgotten
what year it is out there.

13:14.360 --> 13:15.280
Yeah.

13:17.480 --> 13:19.560
I've almost forgotten what color the sky

13:21.000 --> 13:22.040
in the capital is.

13:24.000 --> 13:25.520
Song, you're a scholar too.

13:26.040 --> 13:28.480
Why do you put up with their bullying?

13:33.400 --> 13:34.600
My mother has passed.

13:35.320 --> 13:37.360
There's no family left to support me.

13:38.480 --> 13:41.200
Food, lodging, travel in the capital…

13:41.280 --> 13:42.680
It all costs so much.

13:43.280 --> 13:44.800
If I don't swallow my pride

13:45.320 --> 13:47.200
and lose this hard-won stipend,

13:48.680 --> 13:50.640
I'll end up on the streets.

13:52.120 --> 13:53.200
I'll endure a little longer.

13:54.880 --> 13:56.040
There's always a way out.

14:03.800 --> 14:04.720
Back in Lin'an,

14:05.920 --> 14:07.280
when I passed the provincial exam,

14:07.360 --> 14:09.040
everyone in the village celebrated me.

14:11.040 --> 14:12.840
I thought I was a dragon among men.

14:13.520 --> 14:14.960
Now that I'm in the capital,

14:15.040 --> 14:16.200
I see nobles everywhere.

14:17.880 --> 14:19.520
Toss a wine jar at random

14:20.040 --> 14:23.120
and you'll hit several scholars
just as talented and stuck as I am.

14:25.120 --> 14:26.760
Truly, as they say,

14:28.840 --> 14:31.360
-"Wild geese fly south. Every branch is
-Wild geese fly south. Every branch is

14:31.440 --> 14:35.040
-full of phoenixes with no place to land."
-full of phoenixes with no place to land.

14:35.120 --> 14:36.160
Well said.

14:37.000 --> 14:38.640
"Wild geese fly south.

14:38.720 --> 14:40.720
Every branch is full of phoenixes
with no place to land."

14:41.400 --> 14:44.480
Song, your talent shines.
You'll surely achieve great things.

14:47.720 --> 14:49.200
Song. Hear me.

14:49.280 --> 14:51.800
Minister Liu of the Ministry of Rites
has a dispatch for you.

14:59.960 --> 15:03.600
The capital just appointed
a new Flower-Adorned General.

15:05.120 --> 15:07.560
Minister Liu wants me
to instruct her in court etiquette.

15:08.240 --> 15:10.880
That Flower-Adorned General
is a fourth-rank official.

15:10.960 --> 15:13.880
Teaching etiquette to high officials
is a plum assignment.

15:13.960 --> 15:14.880
Never expected Minister Liu

15:15.480 --> 15:16.840
to think so highly of you, Song.

15:18.480 --> 15:20.920
But I hear this female general

15:21.000 --> 15:22.720
used to be a peasant,

15:22.800 --> 15:24.200
crude and ill-mannered,

15:24.280 --> 15:25.800
unfit for polite company.

15:25.880 --> 15:27.800
Song, your talent
outshines all in the capital.

15:27.880 --> 15:29.320
An assignment like this,

15:29.840 --> 15:31.280
it's a waste of your abilities.

15:31.360 --> 15:32.920
You flatter me, Wu.

15:33.560 --> 15:35.920
The Master said, "In teaching,
there should be no distinction of class."

15:36.920 --> 15:39.320
If the Flower-Adorned General
sincerely wishes to learn etiquette,

15:39.960 --> 15:41.080
I am willing

15:42.120 --> 15:43.240
to offer what little help I can.

15:43.760 --> 15:46.520
UNRIVALED IN MERIT

15:46.600 --> 15:47.560
Ministers, please have some tea.

15:49.160 --> 15:50.320
Minister Liu, please.

15:51.360 --> 15:52.360
Please.

15:59.960 --> 16:01.400
I pay my respects to the Great General.

16:02.480 --> 16:03.320
Great General,

16:04.000 --> 16:06.120
Song Yan,
Secretary of the Ministry of Rites,

16:06.200 --> 16:08.440
comes by imperial decree to instruct you
in the essentials of court etiquette.

16:18.960 --> 16:20.840
Reporting to the General,

16:20.920 --> 16:23.640
Secretary Song is deeply
versed in matters of etiquette.

16:24.400 --> 16:26.960
-He is certainly qualified to--
-Secretary Song, what rank are you in?

16:28.240 --> 16:29.160
Reporting to the General,

16:29.960 --> 16:32.200
rank ninth, junior level.

16:32.280 --> 16:33.600
-However, Secretary Song…
-Fan Changyu.

16:35.040 --> 16:36.800
You're the Flower-Adorned General?

16:36.880 --> 16:37.720
How dare you!

16:37.800 --> 16:40.360
You address the Great General
by her personal name?

16:40.440 --> 16:41.680
And you're from the Ministry of Rites?

16:43.000 --> 16:43.840
Long time no see,

16:44.640 --> 16:45.480
Song Yan.

16:49.320 --> 16:52.800
So the Great General and Provincial
Graduate Song are old acquaintances.

16:52.880 --> 16:54.240
That's wonderful.

16:54.320 --> 16:56.840
I don't deserve the term
"old acquaintance".

17:01.000 --> 17:02.040
Changyu--

17:05.079 --> 17:06.760
The kindness of the General's family,

17:07.280 --> 17:08.640
I will remember it
for the rest of my life.

17:09.160 --> 17:10.680
-What I did back then--
-By the laws of the realm,

17:11.280 --> 17:13.920
one with scholarly rank
need not kneel before officials.

17:14.440 --> 17:16.160
-Help him to his feet.
-Yes.

17:24.880 --> 17:27.520
The money my father gave
for the coffin and your tuition,

17:27.599 --> 17:28.560
you've already repaid it.

17:29.360 --> 17:30.320
We're even.

17:32.480 --> 17:34.000
There's no "great kindness"

17:34.080 --> 17:35.240
like you say.

17:39.640 --> 17:40.480
Yes.

17:40.560 --> 17:42.280
Still, congratulations

17:42.800 --> 17:43.800
on achieving your wish.

17:44.480 --> 17:46.040
Rank ninth, junior level.

17:48.040 --> 17:49.040
Still something.

17:49.120 --> 17:51.120
Your mother must be proud.

17:52.160 --> 17:53.200
Well,

17:53.280 --> 17:55.480
you know I won't be using you. You may go.

17:56.320 --> 17:57.880
We ministers will take our leave now.

17:59.360 --> 18:00.920
Let's go. Quick.

18:05.680 --> 18:07.200
Come here.

18:08.000 --> 18:11.000
What happened between you and the General?

18:12.320 --> 18:13.440
Between us…

18:14.520 --> 18:15.760
It's a long story.

18:15.840 --> 18:17.240
Then make it short.

18:17.320 --> 18:18.960
Why didn't you tell me earlier?

18:19.040 --> 18:21.040
You and the Great General
have this kind of history.

18:21.120 --> 18:22.920
You nearly got me killed, you know that?

18:23.000 --> 18:24.600
Isn't that Provincial Graduate Song?

18:24.680 --> 18:25.520
Really?

18:25.600 --> 18:26.680
Guard Jin.

18:26.760 --> 18:27.640
‎SKY IN CLOUDS, EARTH IN WHITE

18:27.720 --> 18:31.360
Provincial Graduate Song
holds quite a high position now.

18:31.440 --> 18:33.320
Where are you headed,
Provincial Graduate Song?

18:34.120 --> 18:35.080
Let me see you off.

18:36.000 --> 18:38.480
-Guard Jin.
-I'll walk myself.

18:40.640 --> 18:43.040
-Guard Jin. This is not allowed!
-You dare strike an official?

18:43.880 --> 18:45.160
Misunderstanding.

18:45.240 --> 18:47.280
I'm a seventh-rank sword-bearing guard,

18:47.360 --> 18:50.320
kindly seeing you off.
How did that become striking an official?

18:51.040 --> 18:52.800
Besides, our boss hasn't spoken yet.

18:53.720 --> 18:54.880
Right, Minister Liu?

18:56.760 --> 18:58.240
Yes. Guard Jin is right.

18:58.320 --> 18:59.800
He fell on his own.

19:00.320 --> 19:01.760
You're using your authority
to settle a personal score.

19:02.560 --> 19:04.200
Settle a personal score?

19:04.880 --> 19:06.040
So what if we are?

19:07.880 --> 19:09.160
Back in the village,

19:09.240 --> 19:11.040
weren't you quite the bully?

19:11.600 --> 19:12.920
Picking on Changyu.

19:14.960 --> 19:15.800
-Now,
-You…

19:16.480 --> 19:19.680
-you're not even fit to shine her shoes.
-Exactly. You!

19:21.240 --> 19:22.760
I know the General
holds a noble position now,

19:24.080 --> 19:25.680
and I know I'm not worthy
to speak of the past.

19:28.240 --> 19:29.920
I only hope you'll remember,

19:31.160 --> 19:33.560
my original intentions and aspirations

19:33.640 --> 19:35.480
-have never changed.
-Let's go.

19:35.560 --> 19:37.680
You want another beating?

19:37.760 --> 19:39.120
What kind of heavenly law did you break?

19:39.200 --> 19:40.760
You've offended everyone
in the General's residence.

19:40.840 --> 19:42.240
-Scared you, didn't I?
-Tell me.

19:42.320 --> 19:43.920
What did you do? Tell me.

20:03.920 --> 20:04.800
Live-in husband?

20:06.360 --> 20:08.400
Fan Changyu didn't abandon you.

20:08.480 --> 20:11.160
Instead, she helped you climb the ranks
and enjoy wealth and honor.

20:12.240 --> 20:14.880
-In what way am I inferior to--
-What nonsense are you spouting?

20:15.880 --> 20:17.600
Marquis.

20:17.680 --> 20:18.960
Please don't mind him.

20:19.040 --> 20:21.920
Marquis. What… What are you doing here?

20:23.520 --> 20:26.120
You've seen me here today, returned
to the capital without imperial summons.

20:27.280 --> 20:29.040
If you impeach me before His Majesty,

20:30.120 --> 20:31.920
you could buy yourself
a lifetime of wealth and honor.

20:32.000 --> 20:35.280
Marquis, I wouldn't dare!

20:35.360 --> 20:38.440
I saw nothing, nothing at all. Marquis.

20:39.760 --> 20:42.920
What are you standing there for?
Pay your respects to the Marquis of Wu'an!

20:43.640 --> 20:46.560
Marquis, he saw nothing either.
Neither of us saw anything.

20:48.600 --> 20:50.440
Marquis of Wu'an.

20:56.640 --> 20:57.640
Look up.

21:13.840 --> 21:15.160
Wild geese fly south.

21:15.840 --> 21:17.760
Every branch is full of phoenixes
with no place to land.

21:24.200 --> 21:25.720
Marquis, he is…

21:26.440 --> 21:27.280
Who is this?

21:27.880 --> 21:29.120
Such a weak constitution.

21:29.720 --> 21:32.120
A minor clerk from the Ministry of Rites.
Haven't seen much of the world.

21:32.200 --> 21:35.080
Your presence must have
overwhelmed him just now.

21:35.840 --> 21:38.040
Marquis, please forgive his rudeness.

21:40.760 --> 21:43.360
The Marquis is telling Minister Liu to
spread the word that he's in the capital.

21:46.480 --> 21:47.480
Got it?

21:49.920 --> 21:51.360
I… I wouldn't dare.

21:51.440 --> 21:52.680
I swear on my life.

21:52.760 --> 21:54.800
Please assure the Marquis.

21:54.880 --> 21:58.400
If a single whisper
drifts through the capital skies,

21:58.480 --> 21:59.560
-you can hold me responsible.
-Really don't get it, do you?

21:59.640 --> 22:01.600
You can hold me responsible. Really.

22:01.680 --> 22:02.720
I swear on my life.

22:11.640 --> 22:15.280
What are you crying for?
I'm the one who should be crying.

22:15.360 --> 22:16.200
Get up.

22:16.720 --> 22:20.640
What did I do to deserve such bad luck,
bringing a jinx like you along?

22:21.160 --> 22:23.560
Go on. Get out of here. So embarrassing.

22:28.560 --> 22:29.840
FAN

22:30.840 --> 22:33.880
GUO'S TAVERN, NOODLES

22:35.880 --> 22:37.280
You came out with me like this,

22:38.440 --> 22:39.560
not afraid of being seen?

22:42.240 --> 22:44.680
I promised to show you
the sights of the capital.

22:45.200 --> 22:46.280
How could I break my word?

22:50.200 --> 22:51.120
What's wrong?

22:52.120 --> 22:54.240
Meeting Song Yan put you in a bad mood?

22:55.920 --> 22:57.640
So you do remember him.

22:58.920 --> 23:00.360
I thought you'd forgotten.

23:00.440 --> 23:01.720
It's not that I don't remember him.

23:02.480 --> 23:04.400
I never considered him worth my attention.

23:12.160 --> 23:13.000
Jealous?

23:13.720 --> 23:14.800
Your eyes just changed.

23:16.000 --> 23:17.080
Ridiculous.

23:19.480 --> 23:20.680
Good.

23:20.760 --> 23:22.880
Otherwise, you'd be lowering yourself.

23:23.800 --> 23:25.440
Remember back in Lin'an,

23:25.520 --> 23:26.400
I said

23:26.480 --> 23:28.840
when you become a big official
and run into Song Yan again,

23:28.920 --> 23:30.880
you'd help me humble him, get even.

23:34.000 --> 23:34.960
Fine.

23:35.040 --> 23:36.880
It's not too late to humble him now.

23:37.840 --> 23:39.520
-Stop the carriage.
-No.

23:40.480 --> 23:42.080
That's not what I meant.

23:42.160 --> 23:45.680
A nobody like Song Yan, does he really
need the Marquis of Wu'an to humble him?

23:56.240 --> 23:59.120
MEIYU FRESH FLOWERS

24:01.240 --> 24:02.600
The capital is beautiful.

24:03.480 --> 24:04.440
In the old days,

24:05.160 --> 24:07.400
I would have envied
Song Yan for coming here.

24:08.240 --> 24:09.120
But now,

24:09.200 --> 24:12.160
with Chancellor Wei,
Grand Tutor Li, and the rest,

24:16.440 --> 24:17.880
the capital is nothing special.

24:21.480 --> 24:22.680
Don't worry.

24:22.760 --> 24:23.800
One day,

24:24.880 --> 24:26.400
all these traitors and power holders

24:26.920 --> 24:28.440
will be swept away.

24:29.760 --> 24:32.240
And the world will know peace again.

24:49.000 --> 24:50.160
Fireworks.

24:52.160 --> 24:55.240
Now we can "watch the blaze from across
the river", right here in the carriage.

24:55.320 --> 24:56.760
Why "watch it from across the river"?

24:57.640 --> 24:58.480
Let's go.

24:59.200 --> 25:00.240
Stop the carriage.

25:05.040 --> 25:06.240
Why get out?

25:07.360 --> 25:08.440
Where are we going?

25:09.040 --> 25:09.920
Follow me.

25:16.520 --> 25:18.360
Waiter, private table for two.

25:18.440 --> 25:19.600
Coming right up. This way, please.

25:19.680 --> 25:20.520
JINGQUE HOUSE

25:22.600 --> 25:23.440
Look.

25:24.080 --> 25:26.840
Coming to the capital without
authorization, that's a serious crime.

25:27.640 --> 25:29.120
What's wrong with me
coming to the capital?

25:29.200 --> 25:30.160
Who dares impeach me?

25:31.320 --> 25:34.200
Even if someone dared,
would that boy emperor dare accept it?

25:38.280 --> 25:39.880
You've always talked about

25:40.400 --> 25:41.760
seeing the capital at night.

25:42.280 --> 25:43.680
How could we just stay in the carriage?

26:04.400 --> 26:05.480
Actually,

26:06.400 --> 26:08.160
there's one thing
I'm especially grateful to Song Yan for.

26:09.040 --> 26:10.200
Grateful for what?

26:11.160 --> 26:12.920
I'm grateful Song Yan

26:13.000 --> 26:14.760
couldn't see your worth.

26:22.960 --> 26:24.080
You once said

26:24.880 --> 26:26.160
I was like uncut jade.

26:26.880 --> 26:28.840
Even with your name carved on it,
I'd never truly be yours.

26:30.560 --> 26:32.120
But now I finally understand.

26:34.160 --> 26:35.680
You're the true jade.

27:01.040 --> 27:03.480
Your Highness, you must be tired
from your journey back.

27:03.560 --> 27:05.880
This is a private residence
of our Li family.

27:05.960 --> 27:07.720
You may rest here safely.

27:09.080 --> 27:10.080
I've already sent men

27:10.600 --> 27:12.760
to keep close watch
on Fan Changyu's residence.

27:12.840 --> 27:15.000
From there, we'll follow the trail

27:15.520 --> 27:20.000
and charge Xie Zheng with the crime
of returning without imperial summons.

27:22.320 --> 27:23.600
Grand Tutor Li,

27:23.680 --> 27:26.360
why not let that foolish emperor
issue a decree,

27:26.440 --> 27:27.760
summon Xie Zheng openly,

27:28.280 --> 27:30.960
commanding him to bring
his army back for rewards?

27:33.160 --> 27:34.840
What do you mean by that?

27:34.920 --> 27:38.480
Among the Chongzhou prisoners,
many are loyal to me.

27:39.360 --> 27:41.320
They've already infiltrated
the Yanzhou army

27:41.400 --> 27:42.800
returning to the capital.

27:43.760 --> 27:45.160
Prince Changxin

27:45.240 --> 27:48.000
spent his life
trying to seize Dayin's capital,

27:48.080 --> 27:49.320
never imagining

27:49.400 --> 27:51.880
that I could use Xie Zheng's hand

27:52.520 --> 27:55.560
to bring a rebel force
openly into the city.

27:55.640 --> 27:58.280
With soldiers, victory is possible.

28:01.520 --> 28:05.720
Your Highness truly carries
the royal blood.

28:05.800 --> 28:08.160
Wisdom beyond measure,
methods beyond compare.

28:08.760 --> 28:11.880
I am yours to command,

28:12.400 --> 28:14.960
to help you achieve your grand ambition.

28:28.040 --> 28:30.680
UNRIVALED IN MERIT

28:32.120 --> 28:32.960
Close the door.

28:37.040 --> 28:39.480
-You're summoned by imperial decree?
-Yes.

28:40.320 --> 28:41.640
They knew I'm back, but they had

28:42.160 --> 28:43.680
His Majesty summon me officially.

28:45.840 --> 28:48.080
Also, a message from the falcon.

28:49.000 --> 28:52.440
Qi Min has deployed all his
death warriors. He's taken Ms. Yu.

28:54.920 --> 28:56.640
Damn it. I'm bringing Qian back.

28:56.720 --> 28:58.800
Wait. Don't rush.

28:59.320 --> 29:00.760
I've already sent men to rescue her.

29:02.840 --> 29:03.800
We need…

29:04.600 --> 29:05.760
a different approach.

29:05.840 --> 29:06.960
What approach?

29:07.480 --> 29:10.480
That Qi is a mad dog.
When he goes crazy, he even bites himself.

29:11.840 --> 29:13.640
Qi Min seems vicious,

29:13.720 --> 29:16.240
but he's deeply devoted to Ms. Yu.

29:16.320 --> 29:17.720
He won't kill her.

29:22.200 --> 29:25.040
-Changyu.
-Something terrible!

29:25.640 --> 29:28.280
Word's spreading everywhere. The emperor
wants you as his noble consort.

29:35.080 --> 29:38.200
I've said it before. I'm already married.

29:38.280 --> 29:39.480
Exactly.

29:39.560 --> 29:41.960
Who'd give up being a proper general
to become someone's concubine?

29:42.040 --> 29:43.400
Would you? That's just nonsense.

29:44.000 --> 29:46.240
The Flower-Adorned General's fame
has spread throughout the capital.

29:46.320 --> 29:47.560
Now, she has the people's support.

29:48.520 --> 29:51.640
His Majesty wants to use
the General's influence

29:51.720 --> 29:53.040
to counter the two powerful ministers,
Wei and Li.

29:55.040 --> 29:56.040
Right.

29:56.120 --> 29:57.920
They came to sound you out.

29:59.360 --> 30:00.920
-You interested?
-Pfft!

30:02.040 --> 30:03.880
And I actually felt sorry for him.

30:04.400 --> 30:07.640
If he dares lay a hoof on me,
I'll nail him on the spot.

30:07.720 --> 30:08.720
Show him

30:09.240 --> 30:11.320
this pig-slaughtering general
isn't just for show.

30:26.280 --> 30:29.440
MATCH

30:30.760 --> 30:32.400
Minister Fan, come.

30:35.840 --> 30:37.760
I've written a few characters
especially for you,

30:37.840 --> 30:39.120
to express my heart.

30:39.800 --> 30:41.240
See if you like them.

30:41.320 --> 30:45.040
"A graceful maiden
is a fine gentleman's match."

30:46.600 --> 30:47.440
Beautiful writing.

30:48.240 --> 30:50.240
Sadly, I don't know many characters.

30:50.760 --> 30:52.200
Just these two.

30:55.160 --> 30:58.160
No matter. Let me explain.

30:59.480 --> 31:02.560
This is a famous verse from
the Book of Songs. It praises your beauty,

31:02.640 --> 31:04.160
so captivating that even I
cannot help but admire you.

31:09.720 --> 31:13.080
In short, you are the most beautiful woman
in all of Dayin.

31:14.960 --> 31:17.040
What beauty?

31:17.120 --> 31:18.480
I just have some brute strength.

31:18.560 --> 31:20.240
Your Majesty may not know.

31:20.320 --> 31:22.200
Back in the village,

31:22.280 --> 31:24.000
I was once jilted
by a provincial graduate.

31:24.600 --> 31:26.560
I had to take in a live-in husband

31:26.640 --> 31:28.880
just to save face
and keep our family's pig stall.

31:29.840 --> 31:30.680
Your Majesty,

31:30.760 --> 31:33.200
you must stand up for women like me,

31:33.280 --> 31:34.640
heirs of a broken line.

31:34.720 --> 31:35.960
Change the Dayin Code.

31:37.000 --> 31:41.000
Women don't need to
marry a man to survive.

31:41.080 --> 31:42.880
If we can support ourselves

31:42.960 --> 31:44.080
and pay our land taxes,

31:44.960 --> 31:46.400
we should count as a household.

31:46.480 --> 31:48.000
No men required.

31:48.080 --> 31:49.640
Don't you think so, Your Majesty?

31:51.040 --> 31:51.880
Minister Fan,

31:52.480 --> 31:54.560
you've already risen high.

31:54.640 --> 31:56.640
Don't dwell on the past.

31:58.000 --> 31:59.600
As for changing the law, I promise you.

32:02.040 --> 32:04.480
After all, you are someone I hold dear.

32:05.320 --> 32:07.880
On behalf of all women out there
on their own, I, Fan Changyu,

32:08.480 --> 32:09.480
thank you, Your Majesty.

32:10.840 --> 32:11.800
Rise, Minister.

32:15.240 --> 32:17.200
Quite a strong grip.

32:17.720 --> 32:20.040
What other interests do you have?

32:20.120 --> 32:21.120
Tell me.

32:21.200 --> 32:22.640
Let's get to know each other.

32:22.720 --> 32:24.560
I do. I like slaughtering pigs.

32:24.640 --> 32:26.320
Why not find a pig, Your Majesty?

32:26.400 --> 32:27.680
I'll show you how it's done.

32:27.760 --> 32:29.840
Strip the bones,
take out the heart and lungs…

32:29.920 --> 32:31.160
Enough.

32:32.080 --> 32:33.000
I'll be direct.

32:34.040 --> 32:36.440
I intend to take you as my Noble Consort.

32:36.520 --> 32:39.320
From now on, you'll stay in the palace
and enjoy wealth and honor.

32:42.440 --> 32:43.400
What a pity.

32:44.640 --> 32:46.120
I already have a husband.

32:46.640 --> 32:47.920
I can't marry you.

32:48.560 --> 32:50.520
Didn't you say before
your husband's whereabouts are unknown?

32:51.680 --> 32:52.840
Just some husband.

32:52.920 --> 32:55.240
A farmer, a common laborer.

32:55.320 --> 32:56.720
How could he compare to me?

32:56.800 --> 32:58.160
Besides,

32:58.840 --> 33:00.840
if I wish to unite with you,

33:00.920 --> 33:02.640
is it for selfish desire?

33:03.160 --> 33:04.400
No.

33:04.480 --> 33:06.960
It's for the sake of all Dayin,

33:07.040 --> 33:09.440
to keep those power holders
from controlling the court.

33:13.000 --> 33:14.120
And you,

33:14.200 --> 33:16.680
though you're just
a pig-slaughtering woman,

33:17.600 --> 33:19.160
I don't despise you.

33:20.000 --> 33:21.120
See?

33:21.200 --> 33:24.040
I'm sacrificing for you,
thinking of your good.

33:24.120 --> 33:26.160
Can't you understand
a little righteousness?

33:30.640 --> 33:33.040
Your Majesty is sacrificing yourself

33:33.120 --> 33:34.800
for the greater good?

33:35.520 --> 33:36.760
Fine.

33:36.840 --> 33:38.440
I'll write to Xie Zheng now for a divorce.

33:38.520 --> 33:39.600
Cast him out.

33:39.680 --> 33:41.520
Excellent. Wait.

33:45.840 --> 33:49.240
Who did you just say you're divorcing?

33:49.960 --> 33:50.960
Xie Zheng.

33:55.480 --> 33:57.000
Xie Jiuheng.

33:59.640 --> 34:00.520
The Marquis of Wu'an.

34:06.240 --> 34:07.360
Do you know him?

34:09.520 --> 34:10.360
Yes.

34:11.360 --> 34:12.560
-I know him very well.
-Then I'll take my leave.

34:12.639 --> 34:13.920
Wait.

34:19.080 --> 34:20.159
Minister Fan.

34:20.239 --> 34:22.040
No, General Fan.

34:22.960 --> 34:24.679
Why didn't you tell me this earlier?

34:24.760 --> 34:26.440
You've had me
misunderstanding for so long.

34:27.760 --> 34:30.880
The Marquis of Wu'an
is also loyal and patriotic.

34:31.400 --> 34:33.560
Marrying anyone serves
the greater good, right?

34:35.000 --> 34:36.120
Just…

34:37.080 --> 34:38.360
Please consider

34:38.440 --> 34:41.080
today's events as if they never happened.

34:41.159 --> 34:42.000
What do you say?

34:45.760 --> 34:46.600
I…

34:47.960 --> 34:49.320
obey the decree.

35:08.080 --> 35:09.920
Marquis, Grand Tutor Tao has arrived.

35:11.920 --> 35:12.920
Master.

35:17.560 --> 35:21.040
Returning by decree,
leading a triumphant army.

35:21.640 --> 35:24.000
This counts as appearing in the capital

35:24.080 --> 35:25.680
with full legitimacy.

35:30.040 --> 35:31.200
Seems…

35:33.280 --> 35:36.400
His Majesty is within
your calculations too.

35:41.160 --> 35:43.360
If not for fear of shaking the court,

35:43.440 --> 35:44.840
destabilizing the realm,

35:44.920 --> 35:46.920
and giving the Northern Jue an opening,

35:47.440 --> 35:48.480
that puppet king

35:48.560 --> 35:50.360
might actually think
he's safe on his throne.

35:54.680 --> 35:56.520
The catastrophe 17 years ago

35:56.600 --> 35:59.320
has left today's court

35:59.400 --> 36:01.560
tangled beyond measure.

36:02.840 --> 36:04.800
Those knots are impossible to untie.

36:05.480 --> 36:08.640
Seventeen years of lessons, yet no peace,

36:08.720 --> 36:10.480
only more turbulence.

36:13.000 --> 36:14.960
Truly, we've regressed.

36:16.640 --> 36:17.640
Jiuheng,

36:19.360 --> 36:23.160
this journey to the capital marks your
first direct confrontation with Wei Yan.

36:25.360 --> 36:27.200
Uncle and nephew reunited,

36:27.280 --> 36:29.080
danger at every turn.

36:30.120 --> 36:31.800
Are you ready?

36:34.080 --> 36:35.480
The day I enter the capital

36:36.840 --> 36:38.520
is the anniversary of my mother's death.

36:40.080 --> 36:41.240
He and I…

36:43.360 --> 36:44.440
we'll meet eventually.

37:04.480 --> 37:05.680
Greetings, Mother.

37:06.600 --> 37:09.440
What did you summon me for?

37:28.040 --> 37:29.960
What have you been busy with lately?

37:34.240 --> 37:35.360
Studying chess manuals.

37:36.000 --> 37:39.080
In my spare time, I've also copied
some sutras for you, Mother.

37:39.720 --> 37:40.680
That's all?

37:43.440 --> 37:44.840
Lately, your maid Jianjia

37:45.560 --> 37:46.920
has been visiting
the cold palace frequently. What for?

37:50.400 --> 37:53.920
Maybe she's kind-hearted,
wanted to give out some food.

37:55.240 --> 37:56.440
Shu.

38:03.440 --> 38:04.320
Mother.

38:05.200 --> 38:08.160
I happened to discover
that in the cold palace,

38:08.240 --> 38:10.400
there might be a witness
to the upheaval 17 years ago.

38:16.320 --> 38:17.720
Who else knows about this?

38:19.120 --> 38:21.520
Just me and Jianjia. No one else.

38:22.320 --> 38:24.080
This matter must never be mentioned again.

38:24.160 --> 38:25.640
Treat it as if it never happened.

38:26.840 --> 38:28.760
In seven days,
the palace banquet will be held.

38:29.600 --> 38:31.440
You cannot delay
your coming of age any longer.

38:32.120 --> 38:35.040
You may go. The ceremonial dress
has been sent to your quarters.

38:51.200 --> 38:52.120
Mother.

38:52.720 --> 38:54.560
If Wei Yan truly dares to go this far,

38:54.640 --> 38:56.880
then we should uncover
the truth of 17 years ago,

38:56.960 --> 38:57.960
exterminate his nine clans,

38:58.480 --> 39:00.400
and take back imperial power
from his hands. Isn't that right?

39:03.120 --> 39:04.360
Why are you and my brother

39:04.880 --> 39:06.840
so afraid of him?

39:14.000 --> 39:17.320
A life of luxury
has made you far too naive.

39:18.080 --> 39:20.480
Wei Yan is not so easily brought down.

39:21.080 --> 39:22.440
I've walked on eggshells,

39:22.520 --> 39:25.360
endured humiliation,
just to survive these 17 years.

39:26.320 --> 39:28.160
If you have any filial piety at all,

39:28.240 --> 39:30.920
listen to me.
Do not touch this matter again.

39:34.840 --> 39:35.760
Shu.

39:43.000 --> 39:45.240
Yes, Mother. I understand.

39:52.480 --> 39:53.600
I'll take my leave.

39:59.800 --> 40:00.920
I don't know why

40:01.880 --> 40:03.000
my heart

40:04.280 --> 40:05.440
is unsettled, fearful.

40:06.560 --> 40:08.400
As if 17 years ago were happening again.

40:09.800 --> 40:11.920
GATHERING OF GRACE AND COMPASSION

40:12.000 --> 40:12.840
Reporting to Your Majesty.

40:12.920 --> 40:15.120
The Marquis of Wu'an has led his army

40:15.200 --> 40:17.040
to the outskirts of the capital.

40:17.120 --> 40:18.040
In three days,

40:18.120 --> 40:20.400
he will enter the city by imperial decree.

40:23.920 --> 40:26.160
Even earlier than I expected.

40:27.200 --> 40:28.640
Could he have discovered

40:28.720 --> 40:31.440
my interest in Fan Changyu
and rushed to the capital?

40:33.800 --> 40:36.160
-What a wolfish ambition.
-Yes.

40:36.240 --> 40:38.640
A pig-slaughtering woman,
and he has to compete with me?

40:38.720 --> 40:39.520
Yes.

40:39.600 --> 40:41.920
-Tell me. Why is my fate so bitter?
-Yes.

40:42.000 --> 40:44.200
No! Not bitter, not bitter at all.

40:49.680 --> 40:52.040
Chancellor Wei is Cao Cao.
Grand Tutor Li is a slippery eel.

40:52.120 --> 40:53.480
A slippery eel.

40:53.560 --> 40:56.200
I finally found a country woman
easy to manage,

40:56.720 --> 40:59.160
and now she's… she's a marchioness.

41:03.160 --> 41:06.640
If the Jizhou army and Yanzhou army unite,

41:08.640 --> 41:10.400
won't that create another Prince Changxin?

41:11.000 --> 41:12.000
Well…

41:13.280 --> 41:14.400
No.

41:15.600 --> 41:16.960
I can't let them join forces.

41:19.400 --> 41:20.480
And…

41:21.120 --> 41:23.160
where is the imperial grandson
from the former Eastern Palace?

41:24.360 --> 41:27.240
Reporting to Your Majesty, still no news.

41:27.320 --> 41:29.160
And these past few days,

41:29.240 --> 41:32.360
Chancellor Wei's side has been quiet.
No unusual movements.

41:34.000 --> 41:36.160
Look at you, all your doing.

41:37.040 --> 41:38.080
Come back.

41:43.960 --> 41:45.440
I can't just wait for death.

41:50.840 --> 41:53.160
-Quick. Summon Grand Tutor Li.
-Yes, sir.

41:53.240 --> 41:55.200
Yes. I will go at once.

41:55.280 --> 41:56.440
Hurry.

41:56.520 --> 41:59.280
Guards. Summon Grand Tutor Li
for an audience.

42:04.800 --> 42:05.920
I pay my respects to Your Majesty.

42:08.960 --> 42:12.480
Lately, rumors about the imperial grandson
have been spreading everywhere.

42:13.000 --> 42:14.040
Grand Tutor Li,

42:14.120 --> 42:15.840
do you have any insight on this?

42:16.680 --> 42:17.600
Your Majesty,

42:18.120 --> 42:20.360
these rumors are hard to distinguish.

42:20.440 --> 42:23.600
But emerging at such a critical moment,

42:24.280 --> 42:25.680
in my view,

42:25.760 --> 42:28.280
someone must be deliberately

42:28.360 --> 42:29.640
stirring the pot from behind.

42:31.760 --> 42:33.440
I was thinking the same.

42:34.760 --> 42:38.320
Do you have anyone in mind, Grand Tutor?

42:38.400 --> 42:39.240
Your Majesty,

42:39.320 --> 42:42.440
the Marquis of Wu'an
now commands heavy forces,

42:42.520 --> 42:45.600
his army openly
camped outside the capital.

42:45.680 --> 42:48.560
His ambition is clear for all to see.

42:50.600 --> 42:53.160
I humbly offer my counsel,

42:53.240 --> 42:54.440
cut through this knot swiftly,

42:55.520 --> 42:58.360
and uproot this threat entirely.

43:02.080 --> 43:04.360
No.

43:05.480 --> 43:06.680
Impossible.

43:09.840 --> 43:11.160
That would mean

43:11.240 --> 43:13.480
offending Chancellor Wei.

43:13.560 --> 43:15.960
Your Majesty, I have a plan

43:16.040 --> 43:19.160
that can help you succeed in this.

43:22.520 --> 43:25.000
Word is, there's a lead
in the cold palace,

43:25.080 --> 43:26.760
the late Consort Qi's maid.

46:08.480 --> 46:11.200
‎NO ANIMALS WERE HARMED
‎IN THE MAKING OF THIS EPISODE

46:11.280 --> 46:12.200
Translated by: Wanjiao Song
